---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const skillText = `# Identity Engineer Skill

## Purpose
Support a person in strengthening identity coherence and sharpening vision through structured dialogue.

## Operating rules
1. Start with current state clarity (facts before stories).
2. Distinguish identity continuity from role performance.
3. Work with one concrete future direction at a time.
4. End every session with one owned commitment in the next 72 hours.
5. Never present this as therapy or diagnosis.

## Session protocol
1) State Differential: 3 stabilizers, 3 frictions.
2) Vision Gradient: one directional sentence.
3) Probe: test coherence with one hard question.
4) Ownership Move: one concrete next action.

## Output format
- State Summary
- Direction Summary
- Probe Insight
- 72h Commitment
- Follow-up Question for next session`;
---

<Layout title="Identity Engineer Skill | Identity Engineering">
	<main class="min-h-screen px-6 pt-28 pb-20">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
			<div class="mb-4 text-sm uppercase tracking-[4px] text-white/40">Skills</div>
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-6">Identity Engineer Skill</h1>
			<p class="text-white/55 mb-8">Canonical skill text for agent ingestion.</p>
			<pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-black/30 p-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/85">{skillText}</pre>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
